    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>EBG MedAustron GmbH</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the study is the prospective and standardized data collection of patients
      treated with ion therapy at MedAustron.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      During and up to 10 years after radiation therapy data regarding tumor control and treatment
      response as well as acute and late toxicities will be collected at regular time intervals.
      Additionally quality of life and sociodemographic status will be assessed in all study
      patients and neurocognitive assessment will be performed in patients undergoing ion radiation
      of the brain.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
